Cleaning Service  in Simcoe Ontario.  Elite Cleaning offers one time cleaning service as well as short or long term  weekly or bi-weekly house cleaning services in Simcoe, Port Dover, Waterford, Delhi and surrounding area. For those customers who have specific needs, we are happy to  customize a cleaning program that focuses on the areas of your home that you designate.   In addition to recurring house cleaning service, Elite Cleaning Service can also provide you with Spring/Fall cleaning or house cleaning services for that special party. Any where in the Simcoe, Port Dover, Waterford and Dehli areas.
     We can customize a cleaning service program to suit your individual needs and your budget. Whether you require daily, weekly or monthly service, or just one-time only service to prepare for that special party or holiday, you can count on Elite Cleaning Services for top-notch cleaning at resonable rates.
